data.description: OVERSIZED CORNER LOT in the heart of Providence Village!! NEW ROOF installed 2023!! New paint through the entire house. NEW FLOORING. Abundant NATURAL LIGHT gives an open feeling in this well laid out designed floor plan. 3 BED 2 BATH with BONUS 4th room that can be used as a bedroom, FLEX ROOM or OFFICE SPACE!! Huge OVERSIZED kitchen island with upgraded overhead pendant lights. Pull up a stool to your high-end NATURAL STONE counters or grab a chair in your designated dining space. SPLIT FLOOR plan for privacy. Primary bedroom is situated in the rear of home while other 2 bedrooms are on opposite end of residence. Large backyard with CEDAR PERGOLA for shaded afternoons! This MASTER PLANNED AWARD-WINNING COMMUNITY has it all....pool, playgrounds, plentiful walking trails and sidewalks for an active lifestyle! Priced to sell.....don't miss an AMAZING opportunity to live on a corner lot with the benefit of PRIVACY. List of updates can be found in supplements
